description:
Syd Blakovich, ranked 1st, is the bad ass of Ultimate Surrender. At just 5’2, this powerhouse dominates with fear and ability. This Hungarian born athlete lives for destroying hot sexy girls on the mat, then fucking them like a raw animal. If you face this terror, prepare for the fucking of your life.

Devi Lynne is a former collegian wrestler and high school stand out. Since coming to Ultimate surrender, she has been given nothing but the toughest of opponents. At only 102lbs, she has faced the biggest and toughest we have to offer. Devi is relentless, fearless, and has earned her nickname many times over.

This match contains two creatures of nature slamming into each other repeatedly without quarter without surrender.
title: Syd Blakovich "The Nightmare" (10-2) vs Devi Lynne " Spartica" (0-2)
